README for uPortal 1.0 Documents directory

In this directory you'll find documentation for JA-SIG's uPortal
framework.

Manifest
--------

README                    this file
administrators/           directory containing documents of interest to those
                          installing, deploying, administering and supporting
                          uPortal. 
developers/               directory containing documents of interest to those
                          developing content/channels for use with uPortal as
                          well as those who are working on the uPortal 
                          framework itself. 

