Contacting the Author(s)
---------------------

The documentation is coordinated and maintained by Bill Brooks
<wbrooks@lug.ee.calpoly.edu>.

The best way to get your questions about the documentation answered is
to send a message to the mailing list. See
http://www.ja-sig.org/lists/Main.html for information on how to join
the appropriate list.


